---
/**
 * Story Section - Narrative Arc Component
 * Inspired by Brainers storytelling approach
 * Flow: Problem → Solution → Proof
 */
---

<section id="story" class="relative overflow-hidden bg-[#0a0a0f]" data-section>
  <!-- THE PROBLEM -->
  <div class="py-10 md:py-12 lg:py-16 relative">
    <!-- Background glow - smaller on mobile -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 section-bg">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/4 w-[300px] md:w-[500px] lg:w-[600px] h-[300px] md:h-[500px] lg:h-[600px] bg-[#ff3366]/5 rounded-full blur-[150px] md:blur-[200px]"></div>
    </div>


    <div class="container relative z-10 px-4 md:px-6">
      <!-- Section indicator -->
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 md:gap-4 mb-6 md:mb-10 lg:mb-12" data-animate="fade-up">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="w-2 md:w-3 h-2 md:h-3 rounded-full bg-[#ff3366] animate-pulse"></span>
          <span class="font-mono text-xs md:text-sm font-semibold text-[#ff3366] uppercase tracking-[0.15em] md:tracking-[0.2em]">PROBLEM_DETECTED</span>
        </div>
        <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#ff3366]/50 to-transparent"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
        <!-- Text content -->
        <div class="text-center lg:text-start">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl font-black mb-4 md:mb-6 lg:mb-8 leading-tight" data-animate="word-reveal">
            <span class="text-[#9090a8]">כולם מדברים על </span>
            <span class="text-[#ff3366]" style="text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 51, 102, 0.5);">AI</span>
            <br class="hidden md:block" />
            <span class="text-[#f5f5fa]"> אבל מעטים יודעים מה לעשות איתו</span>
          </h2>

          <div class="space-y-3 md:space-y-4 lg:space-y-6 text-sm md:text-base lg:text-lg text-[#c0c0d0]" data-animate="stagger">
            <p class="font-mono leading-relaxed" data-line>
              <span class="text-[#ff3366]">&gt;</span> ארגונים משקיעים מיליונים בכלי AI מתקדמים
            </p>
            <p class="font-mono leading-relaxed" data-line>
              <span class="text-[#ff3366]">&gt;</span> אבל העובדים לא יודעים איך להשתמש בהם
            </p>
            <p class="font-mono leading-relaxed" data-line>
              <span class="text-[#ff3366]">&gt;</span> התוצאה? בזבוז משאבים, תסכול, ופער הולך וגדל
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Warning panel -->
          <div class="mt-6 md:mt-8 lg:mt-10 p-4 md:p-5 lg:p-6 bg-[#ff3366]/5 border border-[#ff3366]/30 rounded-xl" data-animate="neon-pulse" data-delay="0.3">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3 md:gap-4">
              <div class="w-7 h-7 md:w-8 md:h-8 flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center border border-[#ff3366]/50 rounded-lg">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 md:w-5 md:h-5 text-[#ff3366]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-mono text-sm md:text-base font-semibold text-[#ff3366] mb-1 md:mb-2">WARNING: COMPETITIVE_GAP</div>
                <p class="text-[#d0d0e0] text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">ארגונים שלא יאמצו AI בצורה נכונה יישארו מאחור. השאלה היא לא "אם" אלא "מתי".</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Visual element - Data visualization -->
        <div class="relative" data-animate="terminal" data-delay="0.2">
          <div class="relative bg-white/[0.03] backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/[0.08] p-4 md:p-6 lg:p-8 rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_8px_32px_rgba(0,0,0,0.3)]">
            <!-- Glass header -->
            <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 flex items-center justify-between px-3 md:px-5 lg:px-6 py-2 md:py-3 bg-white/[0.03] backdrop-blur-sm border-b border-white/[0.06] rounded-t-xl md:rounded-t-2xl">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#ff3366] animate-pulse"></span>
              </div>
              <span class="font-mono text-xs font-medium text-[#ff3366]/70 tracking-wider">MARKET_ANALYSIS</span>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-6 md:pt-8 space-y-4 md:space-y-6">
              <!-- Stat bars -->
              <div>
                <div class="flex justify-between mb-1 md:mb-2">
                  <span class="font-mono text-xs md:text-sm font-medium text-[#b0b0c0]">ADOPTION_RATE</span>
                  <span class="font-mono text-xs md:text-sm font-semibold text-[#ff3366]">23%</span>
                </div>
                <div class="h-1.5 md:h-2 bg-[#1a1a24] overflow-hidden rounded-sm">
                  <div class="h-full w-[23%] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#ff3366] to-[#ff3366]/50" style="box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255, 51, 102, 0.4);"></div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div>
                <div class="flex justify-between mb-1 md:mb-2">
                  <span class="font-mono text-xs md:text-sm font-medium text-[#b0b0c0]">SKILL_GAP</span>
                  <span class="font-mono text-xs md:text-sm font-semibold text-[#ff3366]">67%</span>
                </div>
                <div class="h-1.5 md:h-2 bg-[#1a1a24] overflow-hidden rounded-sm">
                  <div class="h-full w-[67%] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#ff3366] to-[#ff3366]/50" style="box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255, 51, 102, 0.4);"></div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div>
                <div class="flex justify-between mb-1 md:mb-2">
                  <span class="font-mono text-xs md:text-sm font-medium text-[#b0b0c0]">RESOURCE_WASTE</span>
                  <span class="font-mono text-xs md:text-sm font-semibold text-[#ff3366]">45%</span>
                </div>
                <div class="h-1.5 md:h-2 bg-[#1a1a24] overflow-hidden rounded-sm">
                  <div class="h-full w-[45%] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#ff3366] to-[#ff3366]/50" style="box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255, 51, 102, 0.4);"></div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="pt-3 md:pt-4 border-t border-[#2a2a3a]">
                <p class="font-mono text-xs md:text-sm text-[#c0c0d0] leading-relaxed">
                  <span class="text-[#ff3366]">//</span> רק 23% מהארגונים מצליחים לממש את פוטנציאל ה-AI שלהם
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Decorative elements - hidden on mobile -->
          <div class="hidden md:block absolute -top-4 -right-4 w-6 md:w-8 h-6 md:h-8 border-t-2 border-r-2 border-[#ff3366]/30"></div>
          <div class="hidden md:block absolute -bottom-4 -left-4 w-6 md:w-8 h-6 md:h-8 border-b-2 border-l-2 border-[#ff3366]/30"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>


  <!-- THE SOLUTION -->
  <div class="py-10 md:py-12 lg:py-16 relative">
    <!-- Background glow - smaller on mobile -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <div class="absolute top-1/2 right-1/4 w-[300px] md:w-[500px] lg:w-[800px] h-[300px] md:h-[500px] lg:h-[800px] bg-[#a855f7]/5 rounded-full blur-[150px] md:blur-[200px]"></div>
      <!-- Fingerprint background - right side -->
      <img
        src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dfudxxzlj/image/upload/q_auto,f_auto,w_700/v1765571815/FOCUS_LOGO-06_2_grkja9.png"
        alt=""
        aria-hidden="true"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
        class="absolute top-1/2 right-0 w-[400px] lg:w-[600px] h-auto -translate-y-1/2 opacity-[0.15] pointer-events-none select-none"
      />
    </div>


    <div class="container relative z-10 px-4 md:px-6">
      <!-- Section indicator -->
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 md:gap-4 mb-6 md:mb-10 lg:mb-12" data-animate="fade-up">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="w-2 md:w-3 h-2 md:h-3 rounded-full bg-[#a855f7] animate-pulse"></span>
          <span class="font-mono text-xs md:text-sm font-semibold text-[#a855f7] uppercase tracking-[0.15em] md:tracking-[0.2em]">SOLUTION_FOUND</span>
        </div>
        <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#a855f7]/50 to-transparent"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
        <!-- Visual element first on desktop - Character Image -->
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1 relative flex items-center justify-center" data-animate="scale-up">
          <!-- Glow effect behind character - smaller on mobile -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="w-[200px] md:w-[300px] lg:w-[400px] h-[200px] md:h-[300px] lg:h-[400px] bg-[#a855f7]/15 rounded-full blur-[80px] md:blur-[100px]"></div>
          </div>

          <!-- Character image with fade edges -->
          <div class="relative">
            <img
              src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dfudxxzlj/image/upload/q_auto,f_auto,w_500/v1770417795/0616a06c-820e-4c75-89fd-3f92a1159877_ndhfnn.png"
              alt="חבובוט - הבוט החכם של Focus AI"
              width="500"
              height="500"
              class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-[280px] sm:max-w-[350px] md:max-w-[400px] lg:max-w-[500px] h-auto chavobot-fade"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Text content -->
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 text-center lg:text-start">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl font-black mb-4 md:mb-6 lg:mb-8 leading-tight" data-animate="word-reveal">
            <span class="text-[#f5f5fa]">אנחנו לא </span>
            <span class="text-[#9090a8]">מלמדים תיאוריה</span>
            <br class="hidden md:block" />
            <span class="text-[#a855f7]" style="text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.5);"> אנחנו בונים יכולות</span>
          </h2>

          <div class="space-y-3 md:space-y-4 lg:space-y-6 text-sm md:text-base lg:text-lg text-[#c0c0d0]" data-animate="stagger" data-delay="0.2">
            <p class="font-mono leading-relaxed" data-line>
              <span class="text-[#a855f7]">&gt;</span> צוות המרצים שלנו עובד עם AI בשטח, כל יום
            </p>
            <p class="font-mono leading-relaxed" data-line>
              <span class="text-[#a855f7]">&gt;</span> ההכשרות נבנות סביב אתגרים אמיתיים
            </p>
            <p class="font-mono leading-relaxed" data-line>
              <span class="text-[#a855f7]">&gt;</span> תצאו עם כלים שעובדים ותוצאות מהיום הראשון
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Success panel -->
          <div class="mt-6 md:mt-8 lg:mt-10 p-4 md:p-5 lg:p-6 bg-[#a855f7]/5 border border-[#a855f7]/30 rounded-xl" data-animate="neon-pulse" data-delay="0.4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3 md:gap-4">
              <div class="w-7 h-7 md:w-8 md:h-8 flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center border border-[#a855f7]/50 rounded-lg">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 md:w-5 md:h-5 text-[#a855f7]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-mono text-sm md:text-base font-semibold text-[#a855f7] mb-1 md:mb-2">STATUS: MISSION_READY</div>
                <p class="text-[#d0d0e0] text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
                  <span class="text-[#f5f5fa] font-semibold">אצלנו הפוקוס הוא עליך.</span> אנחנו כאן כדי להפוך אתכם לאנשי מקצוע ב-AI עם כלים אמיתיים ותוצאות מוכחות.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</section>

<style>
  .chavobot-fade {
    mask-image: linear-gradient(
      to bottom,
      transparent 0%,
      black 8%,
      black 85%,
      transparent 100%
    ),
    linear-gradient(
      to right,
      transparent 0%,
      black 5%,
      black 95%,
      transparent 100%
    );
    mask-composite: intersect;
    -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(
      to bottom,
      transparent 0%,
      black 8%,
      black 85%,
      transparent 100%
    ),
    linear-gradient(
      to right,
      transparent 0%,
      black 5%,
      black 95%,
      transparent 100%
    );
    -webkit-mask-composite: source-in;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 40px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.3));
  }
</style>
